description: "A late 19th century map of the Dutch East Indies on four sheets, detailing maritime routes around the region. There are also inset maps showing railways, rivers, roads, and telegraph systems, as well as individual islands and cities. "
label: "Oostkust Sumatra. Schetskaart der Siak Rivier : van het Eiland Tengah tot Siak / opgenomen door H.M. opnemingsvaartuig Melvill Van Carnbee, Commandant Luit. t/z 1e kl. R.O.J. Verschoor."
